  "text": "A critical perspective about both clinically meaningful and practical implications of the proposed operational definitions of maintenance treatment of BD has been outlined by Grunze H. and other members of the WFSBP taskforce (2012), along with the definition of \"continuation\" phase [CITATION_1] .",
